name: There’s Something That Breaking My Head
description:
It's been about 3 months since the last time I listed my work here. If y’all wanna know, I couldn’t draw for my personal needs, NFT, or whatever I enjoy. Like I always feel drained in my mind when I try to do it.

In that time, I didn’t draw other than for work. There are a lot of friends who asked why I rarely draw again, I can’t answer it clearly because I also don’t know what happened to me. In the end, I chose to rest for awhile in the past few months.

It feels good to be back in this space again. Seeing the others have make a lot of progress and made something really cool.

This month, I hope I can continue what I’ve started and rediscovered what was missing from it. LFG!! 🚀🔥
